日本媒体通常称赞游戏的高自由度与战车系统。

系列首作的战车改造、寻找赏金首和高自由度成为当时的话题<ref name="mm2wiivc" />。《重装机兵2》销量超过25万份<ref name="famirev" /><ref name="mm12sale" />，是系列最畅销的作品。《重装机兵回归》售出17万份<ref name="famirev" />。而Game Boy Advance移植版《重装机兵2改》因bug等原因获得爱好者负面评价<ref name="mm2wiivc" /><ref name="ms1impress" />。

《重装机兵 沙尘之锁》分别获得《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》和《[[电击PlayStation|电击PlayStation]]》的30/40分和330/440分<ref name="ms1jprev">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamestats.com/objects/731/731545/articles.html|title=Metal Saga Articles|publisher=IGN Entertainment, Inc.|language=en|accessdate=2013-11-30|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202223316/http://www.gamestats.com/objects/731/731545/articles.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。游戏首周销量6.3万，并成为当周最畅销游戏<ref>{{cite web | url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=5723 | title=Japanese Sales Charts, Week Ending June 12th | publisher=Gamasutra | date=2005-06-17 | accessdate=2013-11-26 | language=en | author=David Jenkins | archive-date=2020-06-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626003522/https://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=5723 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏在北美获一般评价，在评论聚合网站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]汇总分数分别为64%和62%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/ps2/926834-metal-saga/index.html |title=Metal Saga for PlayStation 2 |publisher=CBS Interactive Inc. |language=en |accessdate=2013-11-30 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209015326/https://www.gamerankings.com/ps2/926834-metal-saga/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-2/metal-saga/critic-reviews |title=Metal Saga Critic Reviews for PlayStation 2 |publisher=CBS Interactive Inc. |language=en |accessdate=2013-11-30 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902090704/https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-2/metal-saga/critic-reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]称游戏“有着良好角色扮演游戏的要素，但没有将其结合到一起”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/metal-saga-review/1900-6148659/|title=Metal Saga Review|publisher=CBS Interactive Inc.|author=Greg Mueller|language=en|accessdate=2013-11-30|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021020030/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/metal-saga-review/1900-6148659/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《重装机兵 钢之季节》获得《Fami通》27/40的评分<ref name="ms2famiscore" />。

《重装机兵3》获得《Fami通》33/40分<ref name="mm3famiscore" />。日本玩家称赞游戏可以像《[[勇者斗恶龙III|勇者斗恶龙III]]》那样订制角色，但抱怨游戏容易迷失目标<ref name="4gamerreader" />。《重装机兵2：重装上阵》同样获《Fami通》33/40的评价<ref name="mm2rfamiscore" />。《重装机兵4 月光的歌姬》获《Fami通》35/40的评价<ref name="mm4famiscore" />。
